# Annotation Rules

## WHEN TO USE

- highlight peak or drop
- explain anomaly
- mark important event

## HOW TO USE

- MUST be short (<= 10 words)
- MUST be placed near data point
- MUST include arrow if needed

## EXAMPLE

GOOD:
"Drop due to policy change"

BAD:
"This value decreased significantly because of multiple macroeconomic factors"